          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1649151647140-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1649151647140-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with 1 tbsp <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meat-free mince</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until browned all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1649151652456-x200.jpg",
