      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> into the pan with the <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped ginger</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong></p><p>Cook for 2 min or until fragrant</p>",
